<li>Croft, W. (2002). Typology and universals. Cambridge: Cambridge UP. 2nd ed. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521004993" class="internal">ISBN 0521004993</a>.</li>
<li>Cysouw, M. (2005). <a href="http://www.zas.gwz-berlin.de/mitarb/homepage/cysouw/files/cysouwQUANTTYP.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.zas.gwz-berlin.de/mitarb/homepage/cysouw/files/cysouwQUANTTYP.pdf" rel="nofollow">Quantitative methods in typology</a>. Quantitative linguistics: an international handbook, ed. by Gabriel Altmann, Reinhard Köhler and R. Piotrowski. Berlin: Mouton de Gruyter. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3110155788" class="internal">ISBN 3110155788</a>.</li>
