<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.linguistic-typology.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.linguistic-typology.org/" rel="nofollow">Association for Linguistic Typology</a></li>
<li>Plank, F. Themes in Typology: Basic Reading List. <a href="http://ling.uni-konstanz.de/pages/home/a20_11/plank/TypoThemesBib=2000.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://ling.uni-konstanz.de/pages/home/a20_11/plank/TypoThemesBib=2000.pdf" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li>Bickel, B. (2001). What is typology? - a short note. <a href="http://www.uni-leipzig.de/~bickel/research/papers/manifesto.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.uni-leipzig.de/~bickel/research/papers/manifesto.pdf" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
<li>Bickel, B. (2005). Typology in the 21st century: major developments. <a href="http://www.uni-leipzig.de/~bickel/research/papers/21century_typology_bickel_submitted.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.uni-leipzig.de/~bickel/research/papers/21century_typology_bickel_submitted.pdf" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
<li><span class="PDFlink"><a href="http://www.uio.no/studier/emner/hf/ikos/EXFAC03-AAS/h05/larestoff/linguistics/Chapter%204.(H05).pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.uio.no/studier/emner/hf/ikos/EXFAC03-AAS/h05/larestoff/linguistics/Chapter%204.(H05).pdf" rel="nofollow">Linguistic typology</a></span><span style="font-size:smaller;"><a href="/wiki/Portable_Document_Format" title="Portable Document Format">PDF</a>&#160;(275&#160;<a href="/wiki/Kibibyte" title="Kibibyte">KiB</a>)</span> , chapter 9 of <a href="http://www.uio.no/studier/emner/hf/ikos/EXFAC03-AAS/h05/larestoff/linguistics/" class="external text" title="http://www.uio.no/studier/emner/hf/ikos/EXFAC03-AAS/h05/larestoff/linguistics/" rel="nofollow">Halvor Eifring &amp; Rolf Theil: <i>Linguistics for Students of Asian and African Languages</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://wals.info" class="external text" title="http://wals.info" rel="nofollow">World Atlas of Language Structures</a></li>
</ul>


